<L>__{9. int tom's bedroom night}
<A>__{tom getting more bad news from the answering machine, crossing off yet another firm from the list. few remain. he sits on the bed with his shoulders slumped. for a beat, lost in thought. then, as if to shut those thoughts out, whatever they were, he turns on the tv and joylessly watches the nothingness.}
